From 4dc5afd74c3751eea5985e8d1426867cde1b2343 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 08:54:31 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add semantic navigation actions

Back and Forward found names,
Refresh stopped wearing keycode masks.
Two tabs kept separate lanes,
While history answered what toolbar asks.
